{"tid":1438683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遊行前不斷轉風向嘅問題","createTime":"2019-08-09T23:46:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T01:45:17.000Z","uid":267172,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0f425cbf37d13e318fd4a22161b8aad3f43abb8f","tid":1438683,"uid":267172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:46:20.000Z","msg":"而家警方不停出反對通知書<br />\n今日兩個遊行嘅搞手都話取消<br />\n特別係大埔搞手係極度遲先話取消<br />\n好多人話照去 <br />\n但（至少我本人）完全搵唔到時間地點<br />\n又有post話隨時轉場去機場<br />\n會有大量人唔知去唔去 <br />\n咁樣就會令遊行人數大幅減少<br />\n去左嘅又送頭<br />\n<br />\n星期日又係 一邊話照去一邊話唔好去<br />\n又係唔撚知去定唔去<br />\n<br />\n如果每個星期都係咁就仆街啦<br />\n以後唔洗再遊啦<br />\n有冇人諗下點拆？"},{"pid":"63b8f00a174cb8ad111d53fb9c4158867a102384","tid":1438683,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:47:51.000Z","msg":"推行動post呀<br />\n<br />\n【置頂+廣傳】８.１０ 大 埔 逃 生 路 線 圖 （附 廣 場 名）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438647\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438647</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"96f176c851c03c3ff3e5b6c5bb0fc65b075110f3","tid":1438683,"uid":267172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:49:51.000Z","msg":"自推一下"},{"pid":"1816f88933d61919aee6856e2a41c353e20bfbc4","tid":1438683,"uid":174174,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:50:51.000Z","msg":"咁你要諗吓你去嚟做乜先啦"},{"pid":"ff3bb13da2d5e1cb149613047d6e934346651e5e","tid":1438683,"uid":11698,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:50:56.000Z","msg":"搞手收到反對通知書，唔想孭鑊一定叫你地唔好去保障自己，所以照去就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aacff40ba1ecc481d1cf1644e2824eb068eec12c","tid":1438683,"uid":98431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:52:06.000Z","msg":"對家已經變陣 可以停一停 諗一諗先<br />\n<br />\n大部份人有心理包袱 等呢張垃圾批<br />\n<br />\n放心 民意唔會散 只會爆煲"},{"pid":"c6aee985247a23d7c5f28d1c1def439c84c243ff","tid":1438683,"uid":267172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1816f88933d